@startuml
' Use template styling (assuming monochrome, etc.)
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US2.2.1: Create and Update Vessel Types - System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Authority
participant ":System" as System

activate Authority
'--- Create Scenario ---
Authority -> System : attempts to create a new vessel type with details (name, description, capacity, dimensions)
activate System
System --> Authority : confirms successful creation of the vessel type
deactivate System

'--- Update Scenario ---
... Authority selects an existing vessel type to update ...
Authority -> System : requests to update vessel type details (id, newName, newDescription, newCapacity, newDimensions)
activate System
System --> Authority : confirms successful update of the vessel type
deactivate System

'--- Search/Filter Scenario ---
... Authority wants to search/filter vessel types ...
Authority -> System : searches vessel types by (name or description)
activate System
System --> Authority : returns matching vessel types
deactivate System

deactivate Authority

@enduml
